bilingual.target: 这位捐赠者希望保持匿名。

bilingual.source: The letter came from a nameless donor.
bilingual.target: 这封信来自一个无名的捐赠者。

bilingual.source: The donor chose to give anonymously to the charity.
bilingual.target: 捐赠者选择匿名地向慈善机构捐款。

bilingual.source: The donor's gift will help fund the new library.
bilingual.target: 这位捐赠者的礼物将帮助资助新图书馆。

bilingual.source: The hospital thanked the donor for his generous contribution.
bilingual.target: 医院感谢这位捐赠者的慷慨捐赠。

bilingual.source: Her effusive thanks embarrassed the modest donor.
bilingual.target: 她的过分热情的感谢让谦虚的捐赠者感到尴尬。

bilingual.source: The charity was defrauded by someone posing as a donor.
bilingual.target: 这个慈善机构被一个冒充捐赠者的人欺诈了。

bilingual.source: The research team received funding from a private donor.
bilingual.target: 研究团队从一位私人捐赠者那里获得了资金。

bilingual.source: The school received new computers from a generous donor.
bilingual.target: 学校从一位慷慨的捐赠者那里收到了新电脑。

bilingual.source: The donor gave a large sum of money to the charity.
bilingual.target: 这位捐赠者向慈善机构捐赠了一大笔钱。

yingyinNormal.en: A couple of hours. I have to make some donor calls first.
yingyinNormal.zh: 两小时后，还得先给几个资助人打电话。

yingyinNormal.en: Given your situation, the options with the greatest chances for success would be surrogacy or insemination using a sperm donor.
yingyinNormal.zh: 在这种情况之下，最佳的选择就是代理孕母或是经由捐赠精子受孕。

examination_example.sentence: Most of them engage with potential <highlight>donors</highlight>, since projects that answered questions from interested <highlight>donors</highlight> fared better.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 他们中的大多数都与潜在的捐助者接触，因为这些回答感兴趣的捐助者问题的项目进展得更好。

examination_example.sentence: Most of them engage with potential <highlight>donors</highlight>, since projects that answered questions from interested <highlight>donors</highlight> fared better. And they target a small amount of money.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 他们中的大多数都与潜在捐助者进行接触，因为回答感兴趣的捐助者问题的项目进展得更好。并且他们的目标金额不多。

examination_example.sentence: Scientists have tried to tap Internet <highlight>donors</highlight>, too, with mixed success.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 科学家们也曾尝试利用互联网捐助者，但结果喜忧参半。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2015-2022年8年间全国卷和自主命题省市高考卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2015-2022年全国卷高考试卷，包括阅读、完形、单选、填空、听力、改错、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选各省市考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2015-2022年8年间全国卷和自主命题省市高考卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。
